Package: globalKinhom
Type: Package
Title: Inhomogeneous $K$- and pair correlation functions using global estimators
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2019-09-18
Authors@R: c(person("Thomas", "Shaw", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="shawtr@umich.edu"))
Author: Thomas Shaw [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Thomas Shaw <shawtr@umich.edu>
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), spatstat
Description: This package provides computations to estimate the statistics developed
    in Shaw, M\oller, Waagepetersen. ``Globally Intensity-Reweighted Estimators for
    $K$- and pair correlation functions''. arXiv:2004.00527 [stat.ME].
License: GPL (>= 2)
